#. agencies and on the free movement of such data (hereinafter the
#. Regulation)."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/conditions-bare.pt:68
msgid "conditions_part5_entry"
msgstr ""
"Prelucrarea se bazează pe articolul 5.1 (d),(a) din <a href=\"https://eur-"
"lex.europa.eu/legal-"
"content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2018.295.01.0039.01.ENG&toc=OJ%3AL%3A2018%3A295%3ATOC\">Regulamentul"
